19-2904　　Email：<a href="mailto:press@vrg.jp">press@vrg.jp</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;<!--:--><!--:en--><p>Tokyo, Japan—Venture Republic Inc. (headquarters: Minato-ku, Tokyo; CEO: Kei Shibata; hereafter “Venture Republic”) announced that user access via smartphone of its two travel information sites, Travel.jp and Hotel.jp, is 3.3 times greater than it was last year, and that the total number of visits to the two websites in August 2013 exceeded 8 million.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A</li>\n<li>B</li>\n<li>C</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Travel.jp (<a href="http://www.travel.co.jp">http://www.travel.co.jp</a>/) is Japan''s leading travel meta search. It lets users search and compare the tour packages and airfares from more than 200 online/offline travel agents across the country. It also offers domestic travel guide content (“Tabinesu”) and a tool for searching vacancies on domestic flights in real-time (“Soratan”), among other unique services.</p>\n<p>Hotel.jp (<a href="http://hotel.jp/">http://hotel.jp/</a>) is a user-generated online hotel review service that lets users post pictures, videos and comments about the hotels they stayed in. Users can search hotels based on reviews and ratings, and they can also find deals and offers from multiple travel agencies and accommodation suppliers.</p>\n<p>The popularity of smartphones has exploded in the past few years, and our traffic from smartphones grew to 3.3 times larger than the previous year. Traffic on mobile now accounts for more than 40% of total visits to the websites.</p>\n<p>Visits via personal computer have also increased and the total monthly visits to the two sites in August 2013 totaled 8,013,000, approximately double the traffic they gained the previous year, and the first time monthly visits have exceeded 8 million.</p>\n<p>Travel.jp and Hotel.jp both offer smartphone-specific displays and applications, so that users can efficiently make targeted travel searches on their mobile devices. The sites will continue to provide quality services like these in order to attract even more users.</p>\n<h3><strong>Quote from Venture Republic Inc. CEO, Kei Shibata</strong></h3>\n<blockquote><p>We are very excited to see this exponential growth of our user base driven by smartphones. Our investment over the last 12+ months has really paid off.</p>\n<p>It is clearly only a matter of time before our traffic from smartphones will exceed that from desktop PCs. We continue to maintain our strong focus on mobile and are committed to driving innovations that will allow our users to find the best travel ideas and products quickly and conveniently.</p></blockquote>\n<h3><strong>About Venture Republic</strong></h3>\n<p>Venture Republic operates vertical search engines and product review services, primarily in the area of travel. We help consumers to find, research and acquire the best deals online.</p>\n<p>Travel.jp is Japan’s leading travel metasearch engine. It lets users search and compare tour packages and airfares from more than 200 online/offline travel agents across Japan.</p>\n<p>Hotel.jp is a unique site featuring user-posted pictures, videos, and reviews of hotels;</p>\n<p>it allows users to metasearch accommodations at over 27,000 hotels all throughout Japan.</p>\n<p>- Websites</p>\n<p>Venture Republic Inc. <a href="http://www.vrg.jp/">http://www.vrg.jp/</a></p>\n<p>Travel.jp <a href="http://www.travel.co.jp/">http://www.travel.co.jp/</a></p>\n<p>Hotel.jp <a href="http://hotel.jp/">http://hotel.jp/</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>- Press Contact</p>\n<p>Email: <a href="mailto:press@vrg.jp">press@vrg.jp</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<!--:-->', '<!--:ja-->旅行情報サイト運営のベンチャーリパブリック、 『Travel.jp』『Hotel.jp』の月間サイト訪問数が800万を突破 ～ スマートフォンからのアクセスが前年比3.3倍に ～<!--:--><!--:en-->Venture Republic''s Travel.jp and Hotel.jp reaches 8 million  monthly visitors driven by the growth on mobile; traffic from smartphone 3.3 times greater than