(227, 1, '2014-10-29 10:47:17', '2014-10-29 10:47:17', '<!--:ja--><h2>弊社代表柴田が、APACのオンライン旅行業界におけるインフルエンサーTOP10に選出されました。</h2>\r\nWIT Conference 2014 "Litte Big 10" at Singapore\r\nWarriors : The Top 10\r\nInfluencers in Online Travel in APAC\r\n<div><span style="color: #141823; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, ''hiragino kaku gothic pro'', meiryo, ''ms pgothic'', sans-serif;"><a href="http://webintravel.com/meet-wit-warriors-little-big-10-closes-high/">http://webintravel.com/meet-wit-warriors-little-big-10-closes-high/</a></span></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<h4>柴田啓氏　（ベンチャーリパブリック：共同創設者で代表取締役）</h4>\r\n<blockquote>「ベンチャーリパブリックの創設者で代表取締役。日本から唯一の入賞者となった。日本におけるオンライン旅行業界のパイオニアとして、様々な障壁にぶつかりながらも「Travel.jp」「Hotel.jp」サイトなどを成功させただけでなく、WIT会議の日本開催実現にも多大に貢献。コミュニティの形成や業界発展に大きく寄与した実績が認められた。\r\n受賞に際し柴田氏は”WIT会議はオンライン旅行事業の成長を追及する人々がつながる場”とし、日本の業界拡大にはまだなおこのような場が必要だと考えている、との展望を示した。</blockquote>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><a href="http://humblebunny.com/venture-republic/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/photo_3.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-228" src="http://humblebunny.com/venture-republic/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/photo_3.jpg" alt="photo_3" width="288" height="216" /></a></div><!--:--><!--:en--><p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2>WIT Votes Kei Shibata One Of Top 10 Influencers In Online Travel In APAC</h2>\r\n<p>WIT Conference 2014 "Litte Big 10" at Singapore<br />\r\nWarriors : The Top 10<br />\r\nInfluencers in Online Travel in APAC</p>\r\n<div><span style="color: #141823; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, ''hiragino kaku gothic pro'', meiryo, ''ms pgothic'', sans-serif;"><a href="http://webintravel.com/meet-wit-warriors-little-big-10-closes-high/">http://webintravel.com/meet-wit-warriors-little-big-10-closes-high/</a></span></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<h4>Kei Shibata, CEO &amp; Co-founder, Venture Republic, Japan</h4>\r\n<blockquote><p>Said Siew Hoon, “As a pioneer in his category in his home market, Shibata had to fight many battles – including getting suppliers and customers onboard. He pursued the idea of bringing WIT to his market, believing an event like WIT was needed to grow the industry back home. It took two years of creativity, resourcefulness and partnerships on both our parts to make it happen.”</p>\r\n<p>Kei, recalling his first WIT in 2008, said, “It was like the moment of truth. I realized this is a family and a wonderful network of people dedicated to the pursuit of the growth and development of online travel and I knew Japan needed something like this.”</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><a href="http://humblebunny.com/venture-republic/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/photo_3.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-228" src="http://humblebunny.com/venture-republic/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/photo_3.jpg" alt="photo_3" width="288" height="216" /></a></div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<!--:-->', '<!--:ja-->弊社代表柴田が、APACのオンライン旅行業界におけるインフルエンサーTOP10に選出されました。<!--:--><!--:en-->WIT Votes Kei Shibata One Of Top 10 Influencers In Online Travel In APAC<!--:-->', '<!--:ja-->弊社代表柴田が、APACのオンライン旅行業界におけるインフルエンサーTOP10に選出されました。<!--:--><!--:en-->WIT Votes Kei Shibata One Of Top 10 Influencers In Online Travel In APAC<!--:-->', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '2014-10-29', '', '', '2015-02-09 05:04:05', '2015-02-09 05:04:05', '', 0, 'http://humblebunny.com/venture-republic/?p=227', 0, 'post', '', 0),
